= Aebus - Automatic EC2 BackUp Software

A small gem that allows you to easily automate EC2 backups, included purging of old backups and checking the backup status

=== Configuration



==== Sample

  default:
    backup_time: 00:00:00
    access_key_id: <your_access_key_id>
    secret_access_key: <your_secret_access_key>
    zone: eu-west1
    from_address: <your sender address, must be verified with SES>
    to_address: <a comma separated list of addresses>
    backups:
      daily:
        enabled: true
        keep: 7
        when: 0 3 * * *
      weekly:
        enabled: true
        keep: 5
        when: 0 3 * * 1
      monthly:
        enabled: true
        keep: all
        when: 0 3 1 * *


  vol-1234567:

  vol-7654321:
    backups:
      daily:
        enabled: false
